title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2005-08 Dodge Magnum LED Tail Lights
description: This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto LED Tail Lights on any 2005-08 Dodge Magnum (or Canada-market Chrysler 300 Wagon). This complete walkthrough tutorial guides you through the entire install from start to finish and offers helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
